<reference id="enum_videomirrormodetype">
    <title><ph keyref="VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_TYPE"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc" props="cpp">Video mirror mode.</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="parameters" deliveryTarget="details" props="cpp">
            <title>Enumerations</title>
            <parml>
                <plentry props="cpp">
                    <pt>VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_AUTO</pt>
                    <pd>(0): The SDK decides whether to enable mirror mode.
                        <ul>
                            <li>Local video view: Mirror mode is enabled by default when using the front camera; disabled by default when using the rear camera.</li>
                            <li>Remote users: Mirror mode is disabled by default.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry props="cpp">
                    <pt>VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_ENABLED</pt>
                    <pd>(1): Enables mirror mode.</pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry props="cpp">
                    <pt>VIDEO_MIRROR_MODE_DISABLED</pt>
                    <pd>(2): Disables mirror mode.</pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>